  <T n="name">0xC72A19D1<!--String: "Relationships"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Relationships_1.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:64152876882f2bff</T>
      <T n="text">0x13720DED<!--String: "Spending time with <b><font color='#199C2C'>friends</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>loved ones</font></b> is essential to (most) Sim’s happiness. As your Sim builds stronger bonds with those around them, <b><font color='#199C2C'>new social interactions</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>possibilities</font></b> are unlocked."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Relationships_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:64152876882f2bfc</T>
      <T n="text">0xE4EC0717<!--String: "<b><font color='#199C2C'>Interact</font></b> with other Sims to build <b><font color='#199C2C'>Relationships</font></b> with them. Select the other Sim and pick <b><font color='#199C2C'>Social Interactions</font></b> from the appropriate category (select More Choices in the menu to see the categories).\n\nThe <b><font color='#199C2C'>outcome</font></b> of Social Interactions largely depends on your Sim's <b><font color='#199C2C'>Emotion</font></b>. The Happy and Confident Emotions are great for making friends, while Flirty can improve your romantic advances."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Relationships_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:64152876882f2bfd</T>
      <T n="text">0x9B901748<!--String: "Open the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Relationship panel</font></b> to check on your Sim’s Relationships. Under each face in the Relationship panel, there’s a <b><font color='#199C2C'>bar</font></b> displaying your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>Relationship score</font></b> with that Sim. \n\nIf you attempt to romance a Sim, a <b><font color='#199C2C'>second bar</font></b> will eventually appear. Your Romance and Friendship score can be <b><font color='#199C2C'>different</font></b>; for example, Sims can be enemies and lovers at the same time! "--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
